        <item>
            <title>1.0.2</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 21:07:46 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Fixed @-mention file list showing all files instead of respecting .gitignore
- Fixed @-mention filtering not working (e.g. typing `@cl` now correctly narrows results to `CLAUDE.md`)
- Fixed .git directory and other VCS directories appearing in @-mention file list
- Added Homebrew and Node.js tool paths to subprocess environment so ripgrep works correctly

### Changes
- Improved Sparkle appcast with embedded release notes and delta updates
- Updated documentation
]]></description>
